    <para lang='en'>Click on Add.</para>

    <para lang='en'>Your search criteria is then added to the list of criterias.</para>

    <para lang='en'>The fields associated with items (or copies)</para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>Location</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>Section</para>
