      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <para lang='en'>operate differently and display a list to choose from. To choose two
    or more values simultaneously, hold down Ctrl key and click on the values
    required.</para>

    <para lang='en'>For each criteria, enter one or more words or search expressions.
    Then choose where to find the word or words to search for within the field
    using the list box :</para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>contains at least one of the words</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>contains all the words</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>starts with</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>ends with</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>exactly like</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <para lang='en'>The ISBN field accepts only "starts with" ; fields associated with
    copies of works require only choosing from the list.</para>
