  <section>
    <title lang='en'>Combined search criteria</title>

    <para lang='en'>For every additional criteria, you need to determine the association
    with the various operators : and/or/not.</para>

    <para lang='en'>Criterias add with one another in inverted order : the first
    criteria chosen will be applied last.</para>

    <para lang='en'>You may specify two conditions for one and same criteria, for
    example, Title starts with.... and Title contains the words...</para>
  </section>
